Traditional security often fails in high-tension environments because it creates a "High-Contrast Signature"—a group of tactical-looking men that attracts attention and invites challenge. The DLNTP replaces this with Social Signature Obfuscation. By utilizing mixed-gender crews, decoy transport, and "Star-Topology" communications, the operator manages the HVA as "Encrypted Cargo," moving from the airport to the venue with zero-latency and total environmental blending.
