The DLNTP succeeds by being Inconspicuous but Absolute. By the time a threat realizes a security presence exists, the show is over and the HVA has been extracted via the "Shadow Chain." We do not just protect the person; we manage the environment's logic through the conversion of potential energy into kinetic defense.
